@startuml UseCase_Penelitian_Komparasi
!theme plain
left to right direction

title Diagram Use Case - Penelitian Komparasi Keamanan Container Docker

actor "Admin/DevOps\nEngineer" as Admin

rectangle "Penelitian Komparasi Keamanan Container Docker" {
  usecase (UC1:\nDeploy Container\nBaseline) as UC1 #LightPink
  usecase (UC2:\nDeploy Container\nHardened) as UC2 #LightGreen
  usecase (UC3:\nKonfigurasi Isolasi\nNamespace) as UC3 #LightGreen
  usecase (UC4:\nKonfigurasi Batasan\nCgroup) as UC4 #LightGreen  
  usecase (UC5:\nTerapkan Konfigurasi\nKeamanan) as UC5 #LightGreen
  usecase (UC6:\nUji Enforcement\nCgroup) as UC6 #LightBlue
  usecase (UC7:\nUji Performa\nContainer) as UC7 #LightBlue
  usecase (UC8:\nAudit Kepatuhan\nCIS Benchmark) as UC8 #LightYellow
  usecase (UC9:\nPantau Resource\nContainer) as UC9 #LightCyan
  usecase (UC10:\nGenerate Laporan\nKomparatif) as UC10 #Lavender
}

Admin --> UC1
Admin --> UC2
Admin --> UC6
Admin --> UC7
Admin --> UC8
Admin --> UC9
Admin --> UC10

UC2 ..> UC3 : <<include>>
UC2 ..> UC4 : <<include>>
UC2 ..> UC5 : <<include>>

UC6 ..> UC9 : <<uses>>
UC7 ..> UC9 : <<uses>>

note right of UC3
  - 8 namespace aktif
  - UID remap 0→100000
  - User namespace remapping
end note

note right of UC4
  - CPU: 2.0 cores
  - Memory: 2GB
  - Swap: disabled
  - PIDs: 512
  - I/O: 10 MB/s
end note

note right of UC5
  - Capabilities: 14 → 1
  - Non-root user (UID 1000)
  - no-new-privileges flag
  - Read-only root filesystem
  - Secure tmpfs /tmp
end note

note right of UC6
  - CPU stress (stress-ng)
  - Memory stress (stress-ng)
  - PIDs stress (stress-ng)
  - I/O throughput (stress-ng)
end note

note right of UC7
  - HTTP benchmark (ab)
  - CPU/Memory (sysbench)
  - Startup time
end note

note right of UC8
  Validasi menggunakan
  CIS Benchmark v1.6.0
  Target: ≥80%
end note

legend right
  |= Warna |= Keterangan |
  | <#LightPink>    | Baseline Configuration |
  | <#LightGreen>   | Hardened Configuration |
  | <#LightBlue>    | Testing & Validation |
  | <#LightYellow>  | CIS Compliance Audit |
  | <#LightCyan>    | Monitoring |
  | <#Lavender>     | Reporting |
endlegend

@enduml
